  <title><ph conkeyref="HOS-conrefs/product-title"/>Recommended Hardware Minimums for the Example
    Configurations</title>
  <abstract><shortdesc outputclass="hdphidden">Recommended minimums for disk, memory (RAM), network
      interface, and CPU hardware for several of our example configurations.</shortdesc></abstract>
  <body>
    
    <section id="firmware_requirements">
      <title>Firmware Requirements</title>
      <p>Before performing any installation or upgrade of a <keyword keyref="kw-hos"/> release on
        HPE (ProLiant) servers, the Service Pack for ProLiant (SPP) should be applied to be
        compatible with latest releases in firmware. The Service Pack for ProLiant (SPP) can be
          downloaded from <xref href="http://www.hpe.com/info/spp" format="html" scope="external"/>
      </p>
    </section>
    
    
    
